---
title: Crispy Cauliflower Topped Bean Chilli with courgette and coriander
description: A savoury symphony! This nutritious veggie recipe is packed with exciting elements. Hearty bean chilli, cooling yoghurt topping and crispy cauliflower nuggets to finish the whole thing off.
